title: TV | The Ray D'Arcy Show
text: Ray D'Arcy's show hits Week 2 and already it's looking like he's never been away from our screens. No word yet on who'll be on the couch tonight, but we're still holding out hope that Zig & Zag will turn up as a guest before the series ends. Come on, RTE, we know you're reading this. Give the people what they want and have Zig & Zag appear on the show. The nation demands it.
